#. Tag: para
#: schedulingview.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Scheduling view lets you schedule the projects in your portfolio. The "
"projects are scheduled according to their priority."
msgstr ""
"La vista de planificació permet programar els projectes de la cartera. Els "
"projectes estan programats segons la seva prioritat."

#. Tag: para
#: schedulingview.docbook:7
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set <emphasis>Control</emphasis> to <emphasis>Schedule</emphasis> for the "
"project or projects you want to schedule. Set <emphasis>Control</emphasis> "
"to <emphasis>Include</emphasis> to have resource assignments included in "
"resource leveling. Set <emphasis>Control</emphasis> to <emphasis>Exclude</"
"emphasis> if you want to exclude the project."
msgstr ""
"Establiu el <emphasis>Control</emphasis> a <emphasis>Planificació</emphasis> "
"per al projecte o projectes que vulgueu planificar. Establiu el "
"<emphasis>Control</emphasis> a <emphasis>Inclou</emphasis> per a tenir les "
"assignacions de recursos incloses en l'anivellament de recursos. Establiu el "
"<emphasis>Control</emphasis> a <emphasis>Exclou</emphasis> si voleu excloure "
"el projecte."

#. Tag: para
#: schedulingview.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your projects share resources with projects that are not part of your "
"portfolio, these projects needs to be included for resource leveling to work "
"properly. See <xref linkend=\"content-editor\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Si els seus projectes comparteixen recursos amb projectes que no formen part "
"de la vostra cartera, aquests projectes han d'incloure's perquè "
"l'anivellament de recursos pugui funcionar correctament. Vegeu <xref linkend="
"\"content-editor\"/>."

